        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c7" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;" value="7. Reviewed cards stay linked when one corrects another.&amp;#10;That is truth lineage." vertex="1">
